name: **Inishleague**
description: Inishleague L910-854 Sheet 30 Flat land at N end with house remnants provides excellent camping. Land just E of N tip. Flotsam galore. S side vies for highest boulder clay cliff hereabouts. Lazybeds. December 2008 Otter and Red-breasted Merganser 15 seen, Brent Geese 20 and evidence of grazing by geese all over. Golden Plover 15
